  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Determine the effect of Vancomycin Powder added to the surgical wound at closure on surgical
      infection rates.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study will be blinded and randomized 1:1 to either Vancomycin Powder at closure or no
      vancomycin powder at closure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
